SkillSwap Backend API

A backend system for a skill-sharing platform where users can learn and teach 
lessons based on interests, skill level, and AI-based recommendations.

🚀 Features
    👤 User authentication (Signup / Login)
    📧 Email verification with OTP
    🔐 JWT authentication
    🎓 Role-based access (User / Instructor)
    📚 Lessons system (CRUD)
    🏷️ Interests & tags system
    📤 Upload video + thumbnail (Multer)
    🔎 Filter lessons by interests
    📄 Pagination support
    🧠 AI-ready recommendation structure
    🛡️ Input validation with Joi
    🗑️ Secure delete/update logic
🛠️ Tech Stack
    Node.js
    Express.js
    MongoDB + Mongoose
    JWT (Authentication)
    Nodemailer (Email service)
    Multer (File upload)
    Joi (Validation)